### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003/api/v1
@apiKey = your_api_key_here

### Get Organization Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/organizations
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### List Courses (with pagination and sorting)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses?page=1&limit=10&sort_by=created_at&sort_order=desc
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get Single Course
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/course_id_here
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Update Course
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/courses/course_id_here
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Course Title",
  "description": "Updated course description"
}

### List Course Lessons (with pagination and sorting)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/course_id_here/lessons?page=1&limit=10&sort_by=order&sort_order=asc
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Create New Lesson
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/course_id_here/lessons
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Lesson",
  "content": "Lesson content here",
  "video_url": "https://example.com/video.mp4",
  "duration": 3600,
  "section_id": "section_id_here",
  "order": 1
}

### Get Single Lesson
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/lesson_id_here
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Update Lesson
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lessons/lesson_id_here
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lesson Title",
  "content": "Updated lesson content"
}

### Toggle Lesson Lock
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lessons/lesson_id_here/lock
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locked": true
}

### Enroll User in Course
POST {{baseUrl}}/courses/course_id_here/enrollments
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_id_here"
} 